<a href="https://social.msdn.microsoft.com/Forums/vstudio/en-US/63ae5345-b2ca-45a9-9113-0ddc43e9925b/print-functionality-dialog-less-using-wpf-webbrowser-control?forum=wpf">
вот так</a>).&nbsp;

&nbsp;
